trans-unit.source: Represents the resolution supported by a printer.
trans-unit.target: Представляет разрешение, поддерживаемое принтером.

trans-unit.source: This class is used by the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.PrinterResolutions%2A?displayProperty=fullName> and <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings.PrinterResolution%2A?displayProperty=fullName> properties to get the printer resolutions that are available on the printer and to set the printing resolution for a page, respectively.
trans-unit.target: Этот класс используется <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.PrinterResolutions%2A?displayProperty=fullName>и <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings.PrinterResolution%2A?displayProperty=fullName>Свойства для получения разрешений принтера, доступные для принтера и установить разрешение печати для страницы, соответственно.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings.PrinterResolution%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.PrinterResolutions%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A> property to determine whether the printer resolution type is the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind> value <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>.
trans-unit.target: Используйте <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A>свойство, чтобы определить, является ли тип разрешения принтера <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>значение <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A>

trans-unit.source: If so, use the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.X%2A> and <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Y%2A> properties to determine the printer resolution in the horizontal and vertical directions, respectively.
trans-unit.target: В этом случае используйте <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.X%2A>и <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Y%2A>Свойства для определения разрешения принтера в горизонтальном и вертикальном направлениях соответственно.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Y%2A> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.X%2A>

trans-unit.source: For more information on printing, see the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing> namespace overview.
trans-unit.target: Дополнительные сведения о печати см. в разделе <xref:System.Drawing.Printing>Общие сведения о пространстве имен.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing>

trans-unit.source: `dmPrintQuality` is a member of the `DEVMODE` (device mode) structure, which defines constants that map to printer quality settings.
trans-unit.target: `dmPrintQuality`является членом `DEVMODE` структуры (режим устройства), который определяет константы, которые сопоставляются с параметрами качества принтера.

trans-unit.source: The X property contains the value `DMRES_HIGH` if <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A> is set to <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>, `DMRES_MEDIUM` if <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A> is set to <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>, `DMRES_LOW` if <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A> is set to <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>, and `DMRES_DRAFT` if <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A> is set to <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>.
trans-unit.target: Свойства X содержит значения `DMRES_HIGH` Если <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A>имеет значение <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>, `DMRES_MEDIUM` Если <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A>имеет значение <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>, `DMRES_LOW` Если <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A>имеет значение <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>, и `DMRES_DRAFT` Если <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A>задано значение <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A>
